1
00:01:25,580 --> 00:01:29,930
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,530 --> 00:01:33,910
[Episode 29]

3
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,820
Our intelligence says

4
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:48,430
that Wang Xin has been spotted
in the southeast of the city.

5
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:49,360
Starting today,

6
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,990
all the mills in this area

7
00:01:50,990 --> 00:01:52,650
must be thoroughly searched.

8
00:01:52,890 --> 00:01:54,400
The Patrol Battalion will be stationed

9
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,400
at all major roads in the southeast.

10
00:01:56,650 --> 00:01:58,680
Prefect Zheng will command
from the prefect's office.

11
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,070
Princess Yongci and Princess Yongning

12
00:02:00,070 --> 00:02:02,120
will assist Prefect Zheng
with coordination.

13
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,250
Yes, Your Highness.

14
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:10,330
Except for the officers on duty that day,

15
00:02:10,350 --> 00:02:11,350
Yan Li,

16
00:02:11,350 --> 00:02:12,160
Bai Feng,

17
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,250
Constable Zhan,

18
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,560
you three

19
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,820
take the rest of the men

20
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,110
and go undercover as civilians
for an investigation.

21
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:20,070
Be it a winery, oil mill,

22
00:02:20,070 --> 00:02:20,880
or grain mill,

23
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,540
keep watch on them all.

24
00:02:22,810 --> 00:02:24,370
Report any anomalies you notice
immediately.

25
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:24,860
[Guangshun Mill]

26
00:02:24,390 --> 00:02:25,120
Understood!

27
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,040
Oh, he's fine-looking.

28
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:42,070
Judging from the calluses
on the victim's fingers,

29
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:44,340
he must have been a craftsman
skilled in fine carving.

30
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:45,250
Prefect Zheng,

31
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:47,720
please invite Ning Buyi over
to draw a portrait of the deceased.

32
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,000
Half of his face is gone.

33
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,320
Can he really draw it?

34
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:53,390
Portrait artists must first
master facial contours.

35
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:55,050
Mr. Ning has done this before.

36
00:03:55,350 --> 00:03:56,510
Given his artistic skills,

37
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:57,970
it shouldn't be a problem.

38
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:08,350
Based on the rigor mortis

39
00:04:08,350 --> 00:04:10,080
and the dried blood condition,

40
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:12,020
this person had been killed

41
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,640
before we searched the mill.

42
00:04:15,350 --> 00:04:17,570
The killer set a trap here in advance.

43
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:20,040
This millstone is kind of far
from the door,

44
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,350
and there are no signs of fight

45
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:22,610
or resistance around.

46
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,920
This suggests

47
00:04:24,230 --> 00:04:26,560
the victim willingly walked to this spot,

48
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,779
neither resisting

49
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:29,570
nor attempting to escape.

50
00:04:30,670 --> 00:04:31,790
It indicates that the victim

51
00:04:31,790 --> 00:04:33,120
not only knew the killer

52
00:04:33,790 --> 00:04:35,850
but also trusted him or her very much.

53
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,550
The crime likely occurred late at night.

54
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:50,170
The killer hung the millstone in advance,

55
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:51,000
drew the pattern,

56
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,460
and waited for the victim.

57
00:04:52,770 --> 00:04:54,750
When the victim walked
from the courtyard into the warehouse,

58
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,310
it'd be hard to soon spot
the pattern on the ground

59
00:04:56,310 --> 00:04:57,790
and the hanging millstone.

60
00:04:57,790 --> 00:04:58,870
Meanwhile, the killer distracted

61
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:00,230
the victim's attention on purpose.

62
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:01,840
The victim had no idea

63
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,700
that he was walking to his demise.

64
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:09,880
Judging from the marks on the beam,

65
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,910
the person who cut the rope

66
00:05:10,910 --> 00:05:12,570
was likely hiding on the beam.

67
00:05:17,550 --> 00:05:19,010
Given the cut on this rope,

68
00:05:19,110 --> 00:05:20,970
it should have been sliced twice.

69
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,110
The killer probably
cut halfway through the rope

70
00:05:23,110 --> 00:05:24,570
in advance in case he or she

71
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,400
couldn't sever it in one stroke.

72
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,200
But this smooth end of the cut

73
00:05:28,550 --> 00:05:29,750
was severed in one clean stroke.

74
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:31,610
It looks like it was cut with a saw,

75
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:32,770
but the saw marks

76
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,440
are much thinner
than those of an ordinary saw.

77
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,280
I got it.

78
00:05:44,790 --> 00:05:47,190
It was done with a toothless saw
used by jade carvers,

79
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:49,920
which can precisely control
the depth of the cut.

80
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:51,409
Are you suggesting

81
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:53,280
that the killer is still Wang Xin?

82
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,470
We need the facial portrait

83
00:05:54,470 --> 00:05:55,930
for a final confirmation.

84
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,430
Mr. Ning.

85
00:06:26,350 --> 00:06:27,230
Sorry, guys.

86
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,670
The...

87
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,710
The victim's face

88
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:31,790
is truly

89
00:06:32,230 --> 00:06:33,560
too horrific to look at.

90
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:36,470
I understand.

91
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:38,250
Thank you for your effort.

92
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:40,600
Please draw a portrait of the victim.

93
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:42,030
Mr. Ning,

94
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:43,750
with your artistic skills,

95
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,640
it shouldn't be a problem
to draw the victim's full face

96
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,790
based on his remaining facial features,

97
00:06:46,790 --> 00:06:47,790
I suppose.

98
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:49,360
I will

99
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:50,920
do my best.

100
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,840
You drew it perfectly

101
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:32,520
from just half a damaged face!

102
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:34,520
It's such a waste
that you work for merchants,

103
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,790
Mr. Ning.

104
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:38,010
I'm flattered, Prefect Zheng.

105
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:41,790
Since I have

106
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:43,040
fortunately pulled it off,

107
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,800
I will

108
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,230
take my leave now.

109
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,110
Please.

110
00:07:58,190 --> 00:08:00,480
Just now,
when Ning Buyi was "throwing up,

111
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:03,040
I saw in the water's reflection
that he didn't actually

112
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,640
vomit anything,
only making retching sounds.

113
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,820
I also noticed

114
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,790
that when Ning Buyi drew
Wu Qian's portrait for the first time,

115
00:08:12,790 --> 00:08:14,390
he also retched with nausea.

116
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,570
He had one hand on the coffin

117
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:21,790
and one hand on his leg,

118
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:23,310
with his body bent forward.

119
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:24,790
But someone who suddenly feels nauseous

120
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:26,550
would typically hold
their chest and stomach

121
00:08:26,550 --> 00:08:27,880
to ease the discomfort.

122
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,720
After vomiting,

123
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,230
a person's face or eyes would

124
00:08:31,230 --> 00:08:32,820
usually turn red
from holding their breath

125
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:33,950
with watering eyes.

126
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,460
But that day,

127
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:37,190
his complexion remained normal,

128
00:08:37,190 --> 00:08:38,520
and his eyes were clear.

129
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:43,240
He clearly wasn't afraid,

130
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,409
yet he pretended to be frightened.

131
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:46,840
Ning Buyi

132
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,200
is suspicious.

133
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:36,770
Judging from this,

134
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:37,830
Ning Buyi is very likely

135
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:39,760
the real culprit behind this case.

136
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:42,240
How can you judge
from a suspect's portrait

137
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,310
that Ning Buyi

138
00:09:43,310 --> 00:09:44,190
is the real murderer?

139
00:09:44,190 --> 00:09:46,070
Because the victim of this murder

140
00:09:46,070 --> 00:09:48,310
is actually the carver who fled days ago,

141
00:09:48,310 --> 00:09:49,070
Wang Xin.

142
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,280
I made

143
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:54,000
this clay sculpture
using the victim's head

144
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,790
as a model.

145
00:09:54,950 --> 00:09:56,400
It matches Ning Buyi's first portrait

146
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,640
of Wang Xin.

147
00:09:58,190 --> 00:09:58,920
At that time,

148
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:01,050
he wanted us to track down Wang Xin,

149
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:03,040
so he didn't falsify the portrait.

150
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,920
The thick calluses
on the victim's right fingers

151
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,400
and the scratches on his left hand

152
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,830
prove that he was engaged
in detailed carving work.

153
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:11,230
This perfectly matches Wang Xin's traits.

154
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,880
With Ning Buyi's drawing skills,

155
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:16,120
it's impossible that he couldn't
get the victim's true face.

156
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:18,500
He deliberately
drew Wang Xin as someone else.

157
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:20,430
He must have had ulterior motives.

158
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:22,140
So Ning Buyi

159
00:10:22,430 --> 00:10:24,490
destroyed Wang Xin's head on purpose

160
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,990
and cut the rope
with a jade carver's toothless saw

161
00:10:26,990 --> 00:10:28,500
just to make us believe

162
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:30,070
that Wang Xin was the murderer.

163
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:31,880
To cover up his crime, Ning Buyi

164
00:10:32,310 --> 00:10:33,790
deliberately altered the victim's portrait

165
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,240
to look different from Wang Xin.

166
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,300
Comparing it with my clay sculpture,

167
00:10:37,310 --> 00:10:38,360
it further proves

168
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:41,090
that he already knew
the victim's true identity.

169
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,120
Only someone very familiar with Wang Xin

170
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,120
would know

171
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:45,280
how to make subtle adjustments

172
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,880
to achieve similar facial contours

173
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,280
but a different face.

174
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,400
If he weren't the murderer,

175
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,600
how would he know the victim was Wang Xin

176
00:10:52,710 --> 00:10:54,430
and go to such lengths to conceal it?

177
00:10:54,430 --> 00:10:55,430
But what if Ning Buyi

178
00:10:55,430 --> 00:10:57,760
keeps denying
he drew it wrong on purpose?

179
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:00,080
So we still need evidence.

180
00:11:09,730 --> 00:11:11,110
[Ranmo Gallery]

181
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,520
Isn't it

182
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,430
Lord Yan that I've been

183
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:22,070
missing day and night?

184
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:25,790
And who are you, miss?

185
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:29,430
Your Highness, you've only left me
for a few days,

186
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:31,290
and now you pretend not to know me?

187
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,640
It's only been a few days,

188
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,790
and you've grown even more beautiful.

189
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:36,940
Let's have a drink another day.

190
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:37,980
Yan Li,

191
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:40,830
how dare you cheat on me

192
00:11:40,830 --> 00:11:42,050
and betray my sincere feelings?

193
00:11:42,050 --> 00:11:45,180
I'll go smash the gates
of Prince Yi's Mansion right now!

194
00:11:46,070 --> 00:11:46,590
What...

195
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,040
What's going on?

196
00:11:48,430 --> 00:11:51,160
You didn't even let me explain
before hitting me!

197
00:11:52,470 --> 00:11:53,530
Are you zoning out?

198
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:54,710
Keep acting!

199
00:11:55,930 --> 00:11:57,290
Your Highness,

200
00:11:57,310 --> 00:11:58,640
I'll be waiting for you.

201
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:08,810
Your Highness,

202
00:12:09,190 --> 00:12:11,450
why aren't you going after Her Highness?

203
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:14,360
Given that loud slap,
why should I chase after her

204
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,760
to take another beating?

205
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,470
Her Highness

206
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:18,280
seems to have genuine feelings for you.

207
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,280
Your Highness,

208
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:21,010
if you give her yours as well...

209
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,310
Genuine feelings?

210
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:26,040
I don't have that many to spare!

211
00:12:26,310 --> 00:12:27,350
I see you have

212
00:12:27,430 --> 00:12:29,000
quite a few interesting items here.

213
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,190
I can pick some presents for her

214
00:12:30,190 --> 00:12:31,400
just to calm her down.

215
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:33,640
As it happens,

216
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,570
I recently acquired a small dagger

217
00:12:35,710 --> 00:12:37,640
with a sheath inlaid with seven gems,
quite exquisite.

218
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,370
Her Highness

219
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:39,720
will like it, I think.

220
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:41,180
Fine,

221
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:41,920
that's it.

222
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:44,070
I've left it in my study at home.

223
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,160
I still have

224
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,880
something to handle this afternoon.

225
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:48,190
If you don't mind,

226
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,950
you could condescend to visit

227
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:51,610
my humble abode after dinner.

228
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:52,950
Fine,

229
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:53,970
it's a deal.

230
00:12:56,950 --> 00:12:58,360
Let Bai Feng go in my place?

231
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,040
Why?

232
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:00,960
This mission is too risky

233
00:13:01,130 --> 00:13:02,760
for someone of your noble status.

234
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:03,290
Exactly.

235
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,830
Besides, I know you well

236
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:05,590
with a similar build,

237
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,120
making it more convincing.

238
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,070
No way.

239
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:09,850
Ning Buyi isn't blind.

240
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,790
Given my handsome face and charm,

241
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:13,520
how could you possibly impersonate me?

242
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:13,920
I...

243
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:15,880
How are we alike at all?

244
00:13:18,190 --> 00:13:19,360
What on earth do you want?

245
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,820
It's all for your own good.

246
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,360
I want to go in person.

247
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:23,950
I know best what to do.

248
00:13:24,430 --> 00:13:25,310
As for the danger,

249
00:13:25,310 --> 00:13:26,670
it's dangerous for anyone.

250
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,670
You won't let me go

251
00:13:28,070 --> 00:13:29,920
because you're afraid
I'll steal all the credit?

252
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:30,760
Or is it that

253
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,670
you look down on me
like those people

254
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:34,640
in the capital?

255
00:13:35,070 --> 00:13:36,160
If you're worried about my safety,

256
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,020
Prefect Zheng,

257
00:13:37,100 --> 00:13:38,240
just send more men

258
00:13:38,830 --> 00:13:40,760
to surround that bastard's house.

259
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:41,960
Bai Feng, Zhan Yang,

260
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,710
you two just put in more effort

261
00:13:43,710 --> 00:13:44,910
to get me out quickly.

262
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,040
Ning Buyi is cruel by nature

263
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,170
and cunning in mind.

264
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:52,400
If he finds out our suspicion of him,

265
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:54,150
he might go even more brutal.

266
00:13:54,470 --> 00:13:55,830
You must be extremely careful.

267
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:56,550
In this pouch,

268
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:57,830
the small one is the antidote;

269
00:13:57,830 --> 00:13:58,950
the large one is to heal wounds.

270
00:13:58,950 --> 00:14:00,750
You must not let your guard down.

271
00:14:00,950 --> 00:14:02,010
The eagle whistle?

272
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,040
No.

273
00:14:05,590 --> 00:14:07,240
Chi gave it to you for your safety.

274
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,100
I can't take it.

275
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:09,830
Take it.

276
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:11,280
As long as you're alive,

277
00:14:11,310 --> 00:14:12,430
no matter how severe your injuries,

278
00:14:12,430 --> 00:14:13,630
I can heal you anyway.

279
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,100
Little Wan'er,

280
00:14:15,590 --> 00:14:16,830
you have my full support

281
00:14:16,830 --> 00:14:17,630
as Chi's wife!

282
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,590
Ning.

283
00:14:30,590 --> 00:14:31,640
Stop talking

284
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:34,490
as if we're saying our final goodbyes.

285
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:36,080
Just remember

286
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:37,210
that we will

287
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:40,280
be besties forever.

288
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:42,240
Okay.

289
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,400
Besties forever.

290
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:48,550
It's about time.

291
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:49,950
Let's go.

292
00:15:12,950 --> 00:15:13,550
Please.

293
00:15:23,070 --> 00:15:24,200
This is pretty good!

294
00:15:24,710 --> 00:15:25,880
You're great at making tea.

295
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:27,200
Just a minute, Your Highness.

296
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:27,920
I'm going

297
00:15:27,950 --> 00:15:29,160
to get you the dagger.

298
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,070
Go ahead.

299
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,430
Why is it wet?

300
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:48,600
Stay calm.

301
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:50,620
Can't lose the eagle whistle too.

302
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:55,780
Your Highness.

303
00:16:13,690 --> 00:16:14,310
Oh, no.

304
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:52,430
Ning Buyi,

305
00:16:53,430 --> 00:16:54,720
if you keep coughing,

306
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:57,400
I just can't fake passing out anymore.

307
00:17:19,780 --> 00:17:20,560
Stop!

308
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,800
Kill me if you want to,

309
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:25,460
but don't lust after my nice body.

310
00:17:28,970 --> 00:17:30,119
You woke up pretty fast.

311
00:17:30,119 --> 00:17:31,730
With your puny build,

312
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,640
how much strength could you have?

313
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:35,839
I was just pretending
to be unconscious to play along,

314
00:17:35,839 --> 00:17:37,640
and you really thought you succeeded.

315
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,470
You fool.

316
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,880
You think you can make me end your life

317
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:49,080
in a fast and easy way by infuriating me?

318
00:17:49,750 --> 00:17:50,840
Be patient.

319
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:53,370
I'll avoid your vital spots

320
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:55,250
and use this dagger

321
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,400
to saw your body

322
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:58,870
bit

323
00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:00,300
by bit

324
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,710
until you're split in half.

325
00:18:03,430 --> 00:18:05,560
So you can see your own

326
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:07,710
internal organs.

327
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,320
I never thought I'd die

328
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:12,840
such a heroic death.

329
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:14,180
How thrilling!

330
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:15,090
So

331
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,250
you like being a heroic man.

332
00:18:18,510 --> 00:18:20,770
How could I possibly grant you that wish?

333
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:22,470
How about...

334
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:23,470
Ning Buyi!

335
00:18:24,150 --> 00:18:26,010
Kill me now if you've got the guts!

336
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:34,190
Chi!

337
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:36,170
Where on earth is Yan Li?

338
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:37,800
We've fallen into a trap.

339
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:40,430
Ning Buyi deliberately left
a fake secret passage.

340
00:18:40,430 --> 00:18:42,390
But he couldn't escape this mansion.

341
00:18:42,390 --> 00:18:42,970
Bai Feng!

342
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:43,840
Continue the search!

343
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:44,190
Yes!

344
00:18:44,470 --> 00:18:45,400
Zhan Yang, search the house.

345
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:45,920
Yes.

346
00:18:54,780 --> 00:18:55,500
Yan Chi,

347
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:56,230
look,

348
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:02,510
a secret channel.

349
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:32,030
Ning Buyi.

350
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:36,030
I've never done anything evil in my life.

351
00:19:37,880 --> 00:19:40,270
According to your
Heavenly Way Society's rules,

352
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:41,470
you can't kill me yet.

353
00:19:42,670 --> 00:19:43,990
Heavenly Way Society?

354
00:19:47,550 --> 00:19:48,810
Heavenly Way Society!

355
00:19:49,190 --> 00:19:51,430
So you know
about our Heavenly Way Society.

356
00:19:51,430 --> 00:19:52,640
Very good!

357
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:55,490
Good.

358
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:57,400
Then you should know

359
00:19:58,270 --> 00:19:59,100
that you

360
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:03,400
spent your days in brothels
with seductresses,

361
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:06,030
deceiving Princess Yongning's affections,

362
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:07,190
and you deserve

363
00:20:07,190 --> 00:20:08,710
a sawing-execution!

364
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:11,710
I'm innocent!

365
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:12,840
I'm still...

366
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:16,470
Still a pure virgin.

367
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:19,310
I just fear sleeping alone,

368
00:20:19,330 --> 00:20:20,920
so I visited those brothels every day.

369
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:21,990
I'm deeply in love

370
00:20:22,020 --> 00:20:23,320
with Ning.

371
00:20:23,650 --> 00:20:25,620
We've made a vow to be together forever.

372
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:28,750
We already spent the night together
in the Fengqi House.

373
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:40,410
Say one more lie,

374
00:20:40,430 --> 00:20:42,160
and I'll tear your mouth apart.

375
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:49,920
Come on,

376
00:20:49,950 --> 00:20:50,810
Your Highness.

377
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:55,220
Are you alright, Your Highness?

378
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:57,990
Yan Li!

379
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,020
Where is Yan Li?

380
00:21:05,610 --> 00:21:06,330
This way.

381
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:07,120
He's there.

382
00:21:07,120 --> 00:21:08,390
I'm going to chop you to pieces!

383
00:21:08,390 --> 00:21:09,550
Stop right there!

384
00:21:09,670 --> 00:21:11,060
I'll beat yo up!

385
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:12,250
Get back here!

386
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:14,010
At least His Highness is alive.

387
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:15,420
His way of living

388
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:16,600
isn't easy at all.

389
00:21:56,320 --> 00:21:57,320
Princess Yongci,

390
00:21:58,080 --> 00:22:00,190
when did you start suspecting me?

391
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:03,230
It doesn't matter
when I began suspecting you.

392
00:22:03,230 --> 00:22:05,120
If you hadn't killed Wang Xin
to silence him,

393
00:22:05,120 --> 00:22:06,580
which gave yourself away,

394
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:09,330
my suspicions would have
remained just that.

395
00:22:31,120 --> 00:22:31,950
He

396
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:35,170
brought it upon himself.

397
00:22:35,990 --> 00:22:37,480
I had to kill him.

398
00:22:38,190 --> 00:22:39,920
They all deserved death.

399
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,200
Greedy people

400
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:44,410
should be crushed by stones.

401
00:22:45,230 --> 00:22:47,490
Were you
behind Guanyin Town's case too?

402
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,910
Back then,

403
00:22:48,940 --> 00:22:50,310
my work wasn't perfect.

404
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:52,240
Many things

405
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,590
need to come to an end now.

406
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:58,140
But you formed the Heavenly Way Society.

407
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:05,440
The Heavenly Way Society.

408
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,420
If you want to kill me,

409
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:12,470
then do it.

410
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:16,120
But if I can survive,

411
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,800
I swear I will kill you

412
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:20,750
for the great path!

413
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:25,270
Then tell me

414
00:23:25,670 --> 00:23:27,200
what crime I have committed.

415
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:29,070
The blood on my hands

416
00:23:30,100 --> 00:23:32,110
pale in comparison to the innocent lives

417
00:23:32,110 --> 00:23:33,870
killed in one battle of yours,

418
00:23:34,190 --> 00:23:36,260
Your Highness.

419
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:37,040
How dare you

420
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:39,580
compare yourself to soldiers
who defend our country?

421
00:23:39,580 --> 00:23:41,750
History is written by the victors.

422
00:23:42,610 --> 00:23:44,820
Judge me as you will.

423
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,710
It's just a pity

424
00:23:51,320 --> 00:23:52,380
that my great cause

425
00:23:53,950 --> 00:23:55,150
remains unfinished.

426
00:24:07,570 --> 00:24:09,500
He was determined to kill himself.

427
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:11,690
Let's end

428
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:14,720
this case here.

429
00:24:18,750 --> 00:24:19,410
Close the doors!

430
00:24:19,410 --> 00:24:20,610
Let no one in or out!

431
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:21,400
Yes, sir.

432
00:24:24,050 --> 00:24:25,670
-Don't close the doors!
-Who are you?

433
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:27,160
Open your eyes and look carefully.

434
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,160
I am the Heir of Prince Yi.

435
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:28,800
Open the doors now!

436
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:29,360
Forgive me,

437
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:30,740
Your Highness. Open the doors now!

438
00:24:30,740 --> 00:24:32,120
Yan Li, stop right there!

439
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:33,430
That person's impersonating
Princess Yongning.

440
00:24:33,430 --> 00:24:34,080
Stop her!

441
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:34,470
Yes!

442
00:24:35,750 --> 00:24:36,810
And don't hurt her.

443
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:38,230
How dare you call me an impostor?

444
00:24:38,230 --> 00:24:39,760
-Help!
-I'll kill you!

445
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:45,840
It's him.

446
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:55,540
His skin shows signs
of depleted Qi and blood.

447
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:56,760
Even if he hadn't killed himself,

448
00:24:56,760 --> 00:24:58,490
he would still die in a few days.

449
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:10,710
Seems like this unrighteous flower

450
00:25:10,710 --> 00:25:13,440
is indeed the symbol
of the Heavenly Way Society.

451
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:16,130
No wonder when Zhang Dongxuan
left the Society,

452
00:25:16,130 --> 00:25:17,880
he had to cut out the flesh
from his chest.

453
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:19,880
It was to conceal the existence
of the Heavenly Way Society.

454
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,680
Knowing his days were numbered,

455
00:25:22,510 --> 00:25:23,840
he still went to such lengths

456
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:25,230
to kill so many people.

457
00:25:27,090 --> 00:25:30,290
So this is what they call
"carrying out the heavenly way"?

458
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:36,220
[Capital Prefecture]

459
00:25:38,190 --> 00:25:39,800
The mask is made from camphor wood,

460
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:40,860
painted white,

461
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,800
and carefully crafted to match

462
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:44,460
Ning Buyi's facial features.

463
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,180
Camphor wood is rigid.

464
00:25:46,430 --> 00:25:47,750
Unless someone has exactly

465
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:49,270
the same facial contours as Ning Buyi,

466
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:50,670
no one else could wear it.

467
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,950
And the white color
has faded into dull yellow,

468
00:25:52,950 --> 00:25:54,750
indicating it was made long ago.

469
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:57,720
It seems that you know this mask.

470
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:01,640
The white mask

471
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:04,080
is specific for the Society Leader,

472
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:05,710
while the Deputy Society Leader wears

473
00:26:05,710 --> 00:26:07,030
a silver mask.

474
00:26:07,710 --> 00:26:08,670
So that means

475
00:26:09,510 --> 00:26:12,110
Ning Buyi was
the Heavenly Way Society Leader?

476
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:18,840
Finally, we caught the real culprit

477
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:20,510
behind these murders in the capital.

478
00:26:20,510 --> 00:26:22,970
But other accomplices
have yet to be purged.

479
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:24,920
Ning Buyi is dead.

480
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,760
All we can do is stay on guard.

481
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,740
Prefect Zheng,

482
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:30,360
please dispatch more men
to patrol inside and outside the city,

483
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:32,080
hunting down the Society members.

484
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:33,210
Yes, Your Highness.

485
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:35,080
Master, Your Highness,

486
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:38,320
we've figured out
Ning Buyi's background.

487
00:26:43,370 --> 00:26:45,900
Both River Min and River Qin
suffered flooding.

488
00:26:45,900 --> 00:26:47,640
The court raised disaster relief grain,

489
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:50,300
which Prince Yu
personally escorted to Huzhou.

490
00:26:50,470 --> 00:26:51,950
However, in Huzhou Prefecture,

491
00:26:51,950 --> 00:26:52,920
the Deputy Surveillance Commissioner,

492
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:53,840
Ning Shoude,

493
00:26:54,470 --> 00:26:55,870
embezzled relief funds,

494
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,840
causing failed disaster relief.

495
00:26:57,840 --> 00:26:59,360
Ning Shoude showed no remorse,

496
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:00,430
denied all charges,

497
00:27:00,430 --> 00:27:01,840
and was hence sentenced to death

498
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:02,600
with his property confiscated

499
00:27:02,600 --> 00:27:03,470
and his descendants

500
00:27:03,470 --> 00:27:05,930
barred from taking imperial examinations.

501
00:27:06,430 --> 00:27:07,500
Ning Shoude

502
00:27:07,870 --> 00:27:09,320
was Ning Buyi's father.

503
00:27:10,600 --> 00:27:12,080
As a mere deputy commissioner, no way he

504
00:27:12,080 --> 00:27:13,680
had the guts to embezzle all.

505
00:27:13,710 --> 00:27:14,750
It was only because Prince Yu

506
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:16,160
was His Majesty's uncle

507
00:27:16,160 --> 00:27:17,270
that no one dared investigate him.

508
00:27:17,270 --> 00:27:18,400
His father was merely

509
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,320
a scapegoat for the real embezzler.

510
00:27:20,320 --> 00:27:21,650
With both parents dead,

511
00:27:21,950 --> 00:27:24,350
no wonder he resented heaven's injustice.

512
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,880
Wan,

513
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,730
I need to talk to you.

514
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:39,300
What's wrong?

515
00:27:39,470 --> 00:27:42,520
Did it remind you of the injustice
done to Mr. Shen just now?

516
00:27:42,520 --> 00:27:43,190
Yes.

517
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:46,030
When I think about
those in court who suffered

518
00:27:46,030 --> 00:27:46,920
like my father...

519
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:49,160
Ning Buyi's father wasn't
in the same situation as Mr. Shen.

520
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,620
Though Ning Shoude wasn't

521
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:52,160
the main culprit,
he was not innocent either.

522
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,490
His execution was just.

523
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:56,160
Indeed.

524
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:58,990
If Ning Buyi wanted real justice,

525
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:01,990
he should have tried to make Prince Yu
confess and face punishment

526
00:28:01,990 --> 00:28:03,470
instead of killing commoners

527
00:28:03,470 --> 00:28:05,330
to vent his personal grievances.

528
00:28:05,860 --> 00:28:06,590
I was wrong.

529
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:07,760
You weren't wrong.

530
00:28:07,840 --> 00:28:09,230
You're just way too kind-hearted,

531
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:10,670
putting yourself in others' shoes.

532
00:28:10,670 --> 00:28:11,930
A mistake is a mistake.

533
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:13,680
You don't need to comfort me.

534
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:15,640
When investigating cases,

535
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:17,360
one should never
project feelings onto others.

536
00:28:17,360 --> 00:28:18,470
I jumped to conclusions

537
00:28:18,470 --> 00:28:19,990
without reviewing all the files

538
00:28:19,990 --> 00:28:22,250
and even revealed
my emotions to others.

539
00:28:22,710 --> 00:28:23,600
I did it wrong.

540
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,430
Though Prefect Zheng and Zhan Yang

541
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,650
aren't gossips,

542
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:27,800
in the future,

543
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:30,230
you should still be careful
what you say around them.

544
00:28:30,230 --> 00:28:32,080
Thank you for your candid advice.

545
00:28:32,080 --> 00:28:33,410
It's my biggest fortune

546
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:36,370
to have such a nice husband.

547
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:46,470
I heard that the perpetrator

548
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,840
has been brought to justice.

549
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:48,700
You did well

550
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:50,430
in solving this case.

551
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:52,800
Your Majesty,

552
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:55,430
Princess Yongning
played a significant role

553
00:28:55,430 --> 00:28:57,020
in cracking this case.

554
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:58,780
Prefect Zheng Baishi also

555
00:28:58,800 --> 00:29:00,330
coordinated excellently.

556
00:29:01,560 --> 00:29:03,430
Princess Yongci
deserves reward for her merit,

557
00:29:03,430 --> 00:29:04,710
but you must be punished

558
00:29:04,710 --> 00:29:05,840
for your faults too.

559
00:29:08,430 --> 00:29:10,430
Please enlighten me, Your Majesty.

560
00:29:11,430 --> 00:29:14,990
The suspect of embezzling military rations
has been in the capital for days,

561
00:29:14,990 --> 00:29:15,760
yet

562
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:17,410
the case remains unsolved.

563
00:29:17,710 --> 00:29:19,160
I wonder if you're ignoring

564
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,320
my decree,

565
00:29:20,320 --> 00:29:21,670
merely going through the motions,

566
00:29:21,670 --> 00:29:22,690
or if it's because

567
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:24,710
the internal affairs of the Shuoxi Army

568
00:29:24,710 --> 00:29:26,030
