This lord

856
00:40:35,630 --> 00:40:37,720
is such a good man of integrity.

857
00:40:38,990 --> 00:40:40,030
Did he

858
00:40:40,110 --> 00:40:41,510
gradually lose his sight

859
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:42,670
or was he completely blind

860
00:40:42,670 --> 00:40:44,030
from that day on?

861
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:47,360
I think he became blind from that day,
and the imperial physicians

862
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,820
could do nothing about it.

863
00:40:49,140 --> 00:40:50,280
All these years, Ze's been

864
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,310
searching everywhere
for the best physicians.

865
00:40:52,310 --> 00:40:53,770
But from what we saw today,

866
00:40:54,060 --> 00:40:55,260
he hasn't recovered.

867
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:56,990
Did his eyes

868
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:58,570
suffer any injury before?

869
00:40:59,550 --> 00:41:00,400
No.

870
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,800
Did he have any eye problems before?

871
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:05,070
I don't think so.

872
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:06,550
However,

873
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:08,720
Ze has always been sickly since childhood.

874
00:41:08,720 --> 00:41:09,950
His eyes would hurt if he looked

875
00:41:09,950 --> 00:41:11,210
at things for too long.

876
00:41:11,970 --> 00:41:13,630
If I hadn't been that willful,

877
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,410
how could he have become so ill?

878
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:16,990
I must pay for

879
00:41:17,630 --> 00:41:18,490
my wrongdoing.

880
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:20,840
I want

881
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:23,150
to marry him

882
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:25,760
and take care of him
for the rest of his life.

883
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:26,510
Why?

884
00:41:27,030 --> 00:41:28,880
That was an unintentional mistake
you made as a child.

885
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:30,880
Why should you pay for it
with your entire life?

886
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:32,360
Because no noble lady from the capital

887
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:34,630
would marry a disabled
and idle imperial clansman.

888
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:36,030
Since my recklessness

889
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:38,160
caused Ze to lose

890
00:41:38,200 --> 00:41:40,130
his chance at lifelong happiness,

891
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:41,800
I can't abandon him now.

892
00:41:42,390 --> 00:41:44,390
I must take responsibility for him.

893
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:50,550
But marriage should be based
on mutual affection.

894
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:51,840
You can't let mere compassion turn

895
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:53,240
into lifelong compromise.

896
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:53,880
I...

897
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:57,240
I'm doing this willingly.

898
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:58,500
What about Yan Li then?

899
00:41:58,550 --> 00:41:59,320
Yes!

900
00:42:00,990 --> 00:42:01,880
I don't know.

901
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:03,550
I think

902
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:05,920
even if I'm not around,

903
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,980
he'll probably still enjoy his life.

904
00:42:13,990 --> 00:42:15,390
What else did Fuling say?

905
00:42:17,720 --> 00:42:18,550
She also said

906
00:42:19,240 --> 00:42:21,070
Princess Yongning has made up her mind.

907
00:42:21,070 --> 00:42:22,550
If you don't do something
to prove yourself,

908
00:42:22,550 --> 00:42:23,510
no one can help you.

909
00:42:23,510 --> 00:42:25,450
I was almost hacked to death.

910
00:42:25,720 --> 00:42:27,580
What else can I do to prove myself?

911
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,590
My once untouched body—

912
00:42:29,590 --> 00:42:30,590
she's seen it

913
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:31,550
and hugged it.

914
00:42:31,920 --> 00:42:33,360
Now I've caught a cold,

915
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,630
and where is she?

916
00:42:35,250 --> 00:42:36,810
How heartless she is.

917
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:37,880
She's seen it

918
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:38,920
and hugged it?

919
00:42:39,550 --> 00:42:40,610
When did it happen?

920
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:42,710
That's not the point.

921
00:42:43,240 --> 00:42:44,200
Yeah, yeah.

922
00:42:45,950 --> 00:42:47,280
That's not the point.

923
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:48,310
What matters is

924
00:42:48,470 --> 00:42:49,640
that Her Highness

925
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:51,640
doesn't want to hug you anymore.

926
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:52,360
Bai Feng!

927
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:52,890
However,

928
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,560
Princess Yongci said

929
00:42:54,650 --> 00:42:56,240
a cold can be fatal.

930
00:42:56,470 --> 00:42:58,470
You'd better be good
and drink your medicine.

931
00:42:58,470 --> 00:42:59,470
If you really die,

932
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:02,030
not only will Princess Yongci
have to come examine your corpse,

933
00:43:02,030 --> 00:43:03,110
but Princess Yongning

934
00:43:03,110 --> 00:43:04,840
will also go with the Heir of Prince Xin

935
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:06,450
without any concerns.

936
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:10,510
- Where are you going?
- I'm not dead!

937
00:43:10,510 --> 00:43:11,920
And she's already planning to remarry!

938
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:13,380
Take your medicine first.

939
00:43:14,810 --> 00:43:15,810
She's got

940
00:43:15,840 --> 00:43:17,110
some nerve!

941
00:43:17,140 --> 00:43:17,970
Dream on!

942
00:43:21,350 --> 00:43:23,350
[Prince Xin's Mansion]

943
00:43:28,200 --> 00:43:29,250
I heard from Ning

944
00:43:29,430 --> 00:43:31,400
that you've been in poor health
since childhood.

945
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:32,800
May I ask about the cause?

946
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:37,800
If you wish to cure your eyes completely,

947
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:40,060
you must not hide anything
from your physician.

948
00:43:40,060 --> 00:43:42,110
Otherwise,
even if there's temporary relief,

949
00:43:42,110 --> 00:43:43,320
it will soon relapse.

950
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:46,550
What do you mean, Princess Yongci?

951
00:43:46,550 --> 00:43:48,320
This prescription of oral medicine

952
00:43:48,320 --> 00:43:51,180
only addresses the symptoms
of your organ ailment.

953
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:52,880
But judging from your pulse,

954
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:54,070
there's another cause.

955
00:43:54,070 --> 00:43:55,200
I have an assumption

956
00:43:55,630 --> 00:43:57,320
that might explain why your pulse

957
00:43:57,320 --> 00:43:59,550
doesn't match with your organ condition,

958
00:43:59,550 --> 00:44:01,110
but I need your medical history

959
00:44:01,110 --> 00:44:02,200
to confirm it.

960
00:44:03,430 --> 00:44:05,920
I've long forgotten things
from my childhood,

961
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:07,050
so I cannot tell you.

962
00:44:10,720 --> 00:44:11,590
So,

963
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:13,240
you know that you

964
00:44:13,240 --> 00:44:15,240
were poisoned when you were a child.

965
00:44:22,030 --> 00:44:22,970
Medical fairy,

966
00:44:23,320 --> 00:44:24,950
your expertise is truly amazing.

967
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:26,110
But let the past

968
00:44:26,680 --> 00:44:27,760
be the past.

969
00:44:28,110 --> 00:44:30,240
If I really lose my sight because of it,

970
00:44:30,340 --> 00:44:32,600
then it's just fate playing tricks on me.

971
00:44:37,920 --> 00:44:38,920
Princess Yongci,

972
00:44:40,280 --> 00:44:41,810
please do whatever you can.

973
00:44:43,720 --> 00:44:45,840
Since you have no obsession,
Your Highness,

974
00:44:45,840 --> 00:44:47,240
I will do as you wish.

975
00:44:57,360 --> 00:44:58,220
Your Highness,

976
00:44:58,720 --> 00:44:59,990
please rest early.

977
00:45:07,330 --> 00:45:08,130
Bai Feng?

978
00:45:11,200 --> 00:45:12,060
Your Highness.

979
00:45:13,030 --> 00:45:14,660
Why hasn't Lord Yan Chi returned yet?

980
00:45:14,660 --> 00:45:16,240
His Majesty has some misunderstandings

981
00:45:16,240 --> 00:45:17,400
about Prince Rui
for the military provision case,

982
00:45:17,400 --> 00:45:20,060
so my master had to return
to Shuoxi to handle it.

983
00:45:20,200 --> 00:45:21,930
Then why didn't you go with him?

984
00:45:22,430 --> 00:45:23,360
What if something happens on his way...

985
00:45:23,360 --> 00:45:24,280
Don't worry, Your Highness.

986
00:45:24,280 --> 00:45:26,020
My master knows the road
from Shuoxi to the capital

987
00:45:26,020 --> 00:45:26,920
like the back of his hand.

988
00:45:26,920 --> 00:45:28,250
There won't be any problems.

989
00:45:28,250 --> 00:45:29,330
He left me here

990
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,590
specifically to protect you.

991
00:45:30,590 --> 00:45:31,590
As long as you're safe,

992
00:45:31,590 --> 00:45:32,590
he will be at ease.

993
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:36,900
What brings you here so late at night?

994
00:45:37,110 --> 00:45:38,110
Something's up
at Prince Jin's residence.

